\par "That's about all for the day, wouldn't you say, Brenna darling?" Mick straig
htened up, stretched his back, then glanced over to where his daughter was squatted down painting the floor molding. His lips pursed when he noted she was painting the same six inches over and over with lazy swipes of the brush.
\par 
\par "Brenna?"
\par 
\par "Hmm?"
\par 
